data.description: ADORABLE  spacious 2/1 block home in Palatka. Beautiful original hardwood flooring!  1,161 heating and cooled. Has nice size bonus sunroom that could be used for office, playroom, 3rd bedroom - you decide.  Even has the 'Old Florida' awnings. Metal roof was installed in 2020, new pump in 2021. Huge 1.11 acre corner lot with gorgeous Oak trees and portion of the boundary lined with well established Crepe Myrtle trees. Attached carport with 3 storage areas.  Close to shopping, medical and approximately 3 miles to the City dock and beautiful St. Johns River!
